了房子，但是我结婚也没有打算让加我名字，再一个我俩距离路程半小时，我基本上都是在我妈家住，一个月可能会回去四五次去他家住，反正开车也方便"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/411308570"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2rK/ktby4Il1EAMaCDUzNjc4OTU0ILrIk/kFMA84jgJALXIJNDExMzA4NTcweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1617138415.2833915", "card_id": "Q_320574054", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 45}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "我想了解马克思主义应该读哪些书？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/320574054"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2rK/ktby4Il1EAMaCDMzNTE0NDIwINje3OUFMAI4rgFALnIJMzIwNTc0MDU0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1617138415.2836366", "card_id": "Q_271660970", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 306}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "中考的最后三个月是怎么熬过来的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-e298c0f9a4b8c0943c9f24e848eaf7f3_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "66 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/271660970"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2rK/ktby4Il1EAMaCDIyNjQzOTkyIL/GrdYFMAE4qgVAL3IJMjcxNjYwOTcweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1617138415.2839022", "card_id": "Q_450473110", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 29}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何以「我不想嫁给他了」为开头写一个故事？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "